<h2 id='update-charity-rep-details'>Update Charity Rep Details</h2>
<p>This endpoint can be used to update all details of a charity representative.</p>

<p>On successful completion rep details will be included in the JSON response.</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>http PUT example.com/api/reps/<span class="o">{</span><span class="nb">id</span><span class="o">}</span>
</code></pre></div><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight javascript tab-javascript"><code><span class="nx">TODO</span>
</code></pre></div><h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>PUT example.com/api/reps/2327833979673121796</code></p>
